look like an accident?

10:14.926 --> 10:17.760
No, I'm going to make it look
like an intentional homicide

10:17.829 --> 10:19.830
and leave a trail of clues

10:19.855 --> 10:21.855
all leading back to you.

10:21.900 --> 10:24.033
Of course I'm going to make
it look like an accident,

10:24.102 --> 10:25.134
you dumb ox!

10:25.203 --> 10:26.912
Now act like you've done this before.

10:27.238 --> 10:28.871
I haven't!

10:28.940 --> 10:30.773
Any more notes from the expert, then,

10:30.842 --> 10:33.704
before I go out there and
clean up your stupid mess?

10:33.729 --> 10:34.911
Just get rid of him!

10:34.979 --> 10:36.979
I'll pay your standard rate in the morning.

10:37.048 --> 10:38.047
You have done this before!

10:38.116 --> 10:39.115
What's that now?

10:39.184 --> 10:40.624
Get the [BLEEP] out of my shed.

10:45.590 --> 10:47.123
Hold me closer.

10:47.192 --> 10:48.224
Yes, Madam.

10:52.997 --> 10:54.500
Now kiss me.

10:54.766 --> 10:55.719
What?

10:57.602 --> 10:58.734
Kiss me, damn you.

10:58.803 --> 10:59.770
Madam...

11:09.414 --> 11:10.813
Take me, Peepers!

11:10.882 --> 11:12.415
How would you like to be taken, Madam?

11:12.484 --> 11:14.183
Any way! Every way!

11:14.252 --> 11:15.718
Just tell me what to do.

11:15.787 --> 11:17.053
