11:23.528 --> 11:25.428
- Lady Dodo...
- Yes?

11:25.497 --> 11:27.029
Get that ass in the air.

11:59.731 --> 12:01.964
Dodo, I'm bleeding.

12:03.453 --> 12:04.604
Peepers.

12:04.802 --> 12:06.335
- Don't tell me...
- Yes.

12:07.599 --> 12:09.188
It was my first time.

12:20.815 --> 12:22.115
What's wrong? What's wrong?

12:22.183 --> 12:23.316
