12:32.661 --> 12:34.127
I'll get the police!

12:36.097 --> 12:37.656
Frederick, you old dog.

12:40.468 --> 12:42.540
Good morning.

12:42.825 --> 12:44.892
- We're alive?
- Yes!

12:44.961 --> 12:48.095
