13:03.880 --> 13:07.357
Well, now I thought we could start the day

13:07.381 --> 13:09.281
with a bit of shuffleboard,

13:09.350 --> 13:13.238
and then begin our lives
as we've always dreamt:

13:13.954 --> 13:14.919
together.

13:14.948 --> 13:15.955
Together?

13:15.995 --> 13:16.994
Yes!

13:17.019 --> 13:18.868
Just as we said we would

13:18.950 --> 13:21.698
whilst in the throes of lovemaking

13:21.766 --> 13:25.047
and believing we were about to die.

13:29.908 --> 13:31.908
Okay, sweet Frederick.

13:31.976 --> 13:34.310
