few questions, won't we?

13:34.379 --> 13:37.580
And remember to be
honest, as lies bring cries

13:37.649 --> 13:39.649
to the baby Jesus' eyes.

13:39.717 --> 13:41.951
You killed the foreign
fella, didn't you, Frederick?

13:42.441 --> 13:43.773
What? No.

13:43.847 --> 13:45.613
Don't play dumb with us,

13:45.638 --> 13:47.076
you pockmarked son of a bitch.

13:47.120 --> 13:48.186
Ya murdered him.

13:48.254 --> 13:49.721
